FIFA 22 Ultimate Team ( FUT 22)

James John Morgan · 16h-------- ·
Very unhappy with the Zidane SBC, his lack of agility makes turning feel highly laboured which leaves you resorting to either constant ball rolls or various skills just to gain some space.
His passing is superb (when you have space to pass) and his long shots are brilliant, no matter how good he is in aspects though his lack of movement limits the chances of properly using them.
Overall I personally would tell people to avoid doing his SBC or buying him unless you can get his Prime or moments.
